      "name": "Experimental hemolysis index comparison — Morrison et al. bench data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements from Morrison et al. (2012) FDA benchmark dataset. Mean absolute error 8.3% across five operating conditions; all predictions within ±15% experimental uncertainty band. RH values at 6 L/min / 3500 RPM: CFD = 1.02, experimental = 0.98 ± 0.06."
